            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1687528258871-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1687528258871-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the veg is cooking, combine your <strong>cornflour</strong> and 4 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [6 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp] </span><strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>soy</strong> <strong>sauce</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame</strong> <strong>oil</strong>, <strong>mirin</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>teriyaki sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1687528265439-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
