            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Fable mushroom teriyaki </strong>over the <strong>cooked rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
